List of cities in Italy with more than 50,000 residents
In bold cities that are also provinces administrative capitals.

ISTAT data updated 2007 January 1st [2] . Figures are based on last 2001 census plus data from official bilancio demografico ( demographic balance ) evaluated from 22 October 2001 to 31 December 2006 .
